      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in showroom condition and pampered since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot\u2014not a single scratch or smudge in sight! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car waitlist, this is the one for you. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is ready for its next adventure. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
