    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in immaculate condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the vehicle has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance overhaul, including a dual-VANOS refresh, rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with crisp turn-in and zero bushing play. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory paint depth and original glass. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key example of the ultimate naturally aspirated M-car.",
      "price": 49250.0,
