      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly museum-grade condition. Every inch of the deep, lustrous paint remains factory-flawless, preserved under a climate-controlled cover since day one. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of even the slightest blemish. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder documenting every service interval performed by master technicians. From the pristine undercarriage to the mirror-like finish on the alloy wheels, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
