      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for precise valve timing. The high-revving mill delivers linear power through a crisp six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. This specimen is mechanically impeccable, having received proactive rod bearing service and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains tight, and the engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders. Presented in concours-level aesthetic condition with zero bolster wear or interior degradation, it is a definitive example for the purist collector.",
